title: Missing Maura Murray: Lance & Tim search for answers
itunes:title: Missing Maura Murray: Lance & Tim search for answers
description:
Maura Murray was a 21-year-old college student in February 2004 when she was last seen after crashing her car on a winding road in New Hampshire’s White Mountains. Lance Reenstierna and Tim Pilleri began exploring her unsolved disappearance in 2015, sharing what they’re finding on the "Missing Maura Murray" podcast. Their journey can seem as challenging as the hairpin curve where Murray’s car ran off the road. Tim and Lance are guest on for Thursday’s episode of “Crime Stories with Nancy Grace.”
